# 🎵 Hand Gesture Music Controller (MediaPipe + PyAutoGUI + PyCAW)

Built using:
- [MediaPipe] for hand tracking
- [PyAutoGUI] for controlling media keys
- [PyCAW] for system volume control
- [OpenCV] for camera and UI

## ✋ Supported Gestures

| Gesture                | Action            |
|------------------------|-------------------|
| All fingers down       | Play/Pause        |
| Only index finger up   | Next Song         |
| Index + Middle up      | Previous Song     |
| Only thumb up          | Volume Up         |
| Only pinky up          | Volume Down       |


## 🛠️ Setup

### 1. Install dependencies

```bash
pip install opencv-python mediapipe pyautogui pycaw comtypes